  "keyFeatures": [
    "Structured radiology report authoring with customizable templates",
    "Integrated DICOM viewer for image review alongside reporting",
    "Worklist management for tracking pending and completed studies",
    "HL7/FHIR integration for EMR/RIS interoperability",
    "Role-based access control for radiologists, residents, and technologists",
    "Real-time notifications for report status changes",
    "Audit trail and report versioning",
    "Multi-environment deployment (dev, staging, production)"
